Create new package name
lerna create [package-name ex: common-ui-button]

Add new library package like react in package
lerna add [package-name ex: react] [where want to add ex: package/common-ui-button]

Publish new package without git
lerna publish --force-publish=@crate/common-ui-button --no-git-tag-version --no-push

